==========
 GREETING 
==========
| 

about
-----
| 

:author:  Bart Thate <bthate@gmail.com>
:contact: IRCNET/#dunkbots
:distribution: core
:license: Public Domain
 
| 

description
-----------
| 

the greeting plugin allows users to set messages to be said when they join a channel

| 

  say greet message when user joins 

| 

commands
--------
| 

1) *greeting-add*

    :description: add greeting message

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !greeting-add yooo dudes
        <output> greeting message added


2) *greeting-cfg*

    :description: plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !greeting-cfg
        <output> options: enable=[] .. version="GOZERBOT 0.9"


3) *greeting-cfgsave*

    :description: save plugin configuration

    :permissions: OPER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !greeting-cfgsave
        <output> config saved


4) *greeting-del*

    :description: delete greeting message

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !greeting-delete 1
        <output> none
5) *greeting-list*

    :description: show greetings of user

    :permissions: USER

    :examples:

    ::

        <user> !greeting-list
        <output> yooo dudes


